                                <h1 class="">Why ERP sucks</h1>
                                <p>For some reason, ERP software hasn't evolved at the same rate as most modern consumer software. What's worse is that there are millions of people who use this irritating, outdated, and infuriating software every day. But just because something is powerful, doesn't mean it has to be complicated.</p>
                                <p>Basically, people hate ERP systems. </p>
