                            <h2>Frustrating and ugly</h2>
                            <p>Software tools are supposed to be designed to help people do their job. The fact that these systems are confusing,  cumbersome, and unintuitive makes getting tasks done excruciatingly painful. So much so that using ERP software can actually get in the way of getting the job done.</p><a href="reinventing-erp.html" class="" ><button class="btn btn-warning">How we're fixing it</button></a>
