                            <p>Implementations are pricey. There is a massive upfront cost related to the software, not to mention the fees related to training, conversion, and consulting, and don’t forget the hardware.</p><a href="reinventing-erp.html" class="" ><button class="btn btn-warning">How we're fixing it</button></a>
